 = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Aura of Abjuration</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f00; background-color: #fcc; border-left: 15px solid #f00; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Obsolete</b>: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.</i></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:18em;\">\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"> <a href=\"/File:Aura_of_abjuration.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Aura of abjuration.png\" src=\"/images/c/c6/Aura_of_abjuration.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#8195;Aura of Abjuration\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Level\n</th>\n<td> 5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>1</sup>\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Summonings\" title=\"Summonings\">Summoning</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n\n\n\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Source(s)\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Book_of_Summonings\" title=\"Book of Summonings\">Book of Summonings</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Casting noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Spell noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 0\n</td></tr>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</table></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Continuously abjures hostile summoned creatures in the vicinity of the caster. This reduces their remaining time before being sent back where they came from.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Aura of Abjuration</b> is a level 5 <a href=\"/Summonings\" title=\"Summonings\">Summoning</a> spell which gives you an abjuration <a href=\"/Aura\" title=\"Aura\">aura</a>. Any hostile summoned creatures within its range will have their duration reduced each turn, and will be dismissed entirely when their duration hits 0.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<ul><li>You can cast this spell before combat with a summoner. This is usually worthwhile against opponents that have other means of hurting you badly from behind their summons; think <a href=\"/Royal_mummy\" title=\"Royal mummy\">greater mummies</a> and <a href=\"/Lich\" title=\"Lich\">liches</a>. In the mid-game, the spell works well against <a href=\"/Deep_elf_demonologist\" title=\"Deep elf demonologist\">deep elf demonologists</a>, <a href=\"/Boggart\" title=\"Boggart\">boggarts</a>, and <a href=\"/Vampire_mage\" title=\"Vampire mage\">vampire magi</a>.</li>\n<li>Note that the spell has no effect on <a href=\"/Durable_summon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Durable summon\">durable summons</a> or <a href=\"/Eldritch_tentacle\" title=\"Eldritch tentacle\">eldritch tentacles</a>. Also, <a href=\"/The_Shining_One\" title=\"The Shining One\">The Shining One</a> protects <a href=\"/Seraph\" title=\"Seraph\">Seraph</a>'s <a href=\"/Summon_Holies\" title=\"Summon Holies\">divine summons</a> against abjuration.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>The spell was removed in <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a>.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.17\" title=\"0.17\">0.17</a>, Aura of Abjuration was a level 6 spell and appeared solely in <a href=\"/Grand_Grimoire\" title=\"Grand Grimoire\">Grand Grimoire</a>.</li>\n<li>Aura of Abjuration was added in <a href=\"/0.14\" title=\"0.14\">0.14</a>, replacing <a href=\"/Mass_Abjuration\" title=\"Mass Abjuration\">Mass Abjuration</a>.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916182709\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.116 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.395 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 131/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 671/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1422/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 273/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.020s\nLua virtual size: 8.14 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  329.957      1 -total\n 94.46%  311.666      1 Template:Spell\n 73.40%  242.183      8 Template:If\n 12.14%   40.071      1 Template:Summonings\n  3.10%   10.239      1 Template:Obsolete\n  2.24%    7.385      1 Template:Flavour\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:7419-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916182708 and revision id 54207\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Aura_of_Abjuration&amp;oldid=54207\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Aura_of_Abjuration&amp;oldid=54207</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"m